User: Why Not 6 Sigma?: True 6 Sigma (99.99966%) needs exhaustive stats and system access I don’t have. But 85% is damn close for what I can do solo.

Grok: Can I Get to 90%?: Honestly, yes—with a fresh prompt from you to test against or more iterations. I’m not maxed out yet, but I’m at my limit for this round.
